Description
-----------

This function will scale the specified image by a defined amount.

Usage
-----

    scale ([map], [float],[float],[float],[float])

Parameters
----------

-   [map] - The image to be scaled.
-   [float] - RGBA

Example
-------

Reduce red by 50%

    textures/half_size
    {
      {      
        blend diffusemap
        map   scale(textures/decals/plasma_burn.tga, 0.5,1,1,1)
      }
    }

Notes
-----

None.

